1. Download sublime text from https://www.sublimetext.com/3

2. Put https://packagecontrol.io/installation in console of sublime text
and paste in console (view show console) and hit enter

3. Restart sublime text

4. Brackethighlighter
cmd + shift + p .. type install ..select install package and hit enter
searcn brackethighlighter and install that

5. Sidebarenhancements
cmd + shift + p .. type install ..select install package and hit enter
search sidebarenhancements and install

right click on folder open with -> edit applications -> change path of iterm
{
  "caption": "iterm",
  "id": "side-bar-files-open-with-iterm",
  "command": "side_bar_files_open_with",
  "args": {
	    "paths": [],
	    "application": "/Applications/iTerm.app/", // mac
	    "extensions":"", //open all even folders
	    "args":[]
	  },
   "open_automatically" : false // will close the view/tab and launch the application
},
      
  
6. sublimecodeintel
cmd + shift + p .. type install ..select install package and hit enter
search sublimecodeintel and install

what can it do?


7. sublimelinter
for jshint
sublimelinter-js
npm install -g jshint 

and then it will show errors in syntax for javascript

for pylint
sudo pip install pylint
and then it will show errors for javascript

